### Create a new project
POST https://localhost:7001/api/Project
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "My New Project"
}

### Get all projects
GET https://localhost:7001/api/Project

### Get a specific project (replace {id} with actual project ID)
GET https://localhost:7001/api/Project/{id}

### Update a project (replace {id} with actual project ID)
PUT https://localhost:7001/api/Project/{id}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Updated Project Name"
}

### Delete a project (replace {id} with actual project ID)
DELETE https://localhost:7001/api/Project/{id} 